        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 500">KKR Sees Huge Data Center Growth</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">KKR projects annual global data center spending to hit <a href="https://www.bnnbloomberg.ca/business/technology/2024/11/01/kkr-sees-250-billion-of-annual-spending-from-data-center-boom/" target="_blank">$250 billion</a>, driven by AI and cloud growth. The US leads in power consumption for data centers, using 16-18 gigawatts. KKR’s $50 billion partnership with Energy Capital Partners will fuel development across power and infrastructure. Competitors like Blackstone and Brookfield are also investing heavily, marking data centers as a key growth area. The sector’s shift from “just-in-time” power sourcing to guaranteed power access underscores its importance as tech giants expand their infrastructure.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
